{
  "stem": "25114.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "How did you get this letter?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, he said I went-- somewhere in a-- in a place, where there's a lot of partisans, they were in a-- since they were women, my sister could sew.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one of the peasants took her in and gave them food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she did for the-- it was a nice young couple after the marriage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave them food, and they kept them in their place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my sister wanted to join the partisans-- my both sisters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So once a partisan came in, and she said-- she said, I've got my sister and my brother-in-law in the Bielski partisan.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you ever meet them, could you give them a letter?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all by chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you ever meet them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it happened at this particular time, that they happened to ride right through it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would have never seen this letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He just had arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He sees people, sitting near a pathway, and said, who is that?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, that's Bielski's Otriad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, oh, Bielski's Otriad?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I've got a letter for someone from Bielski's Otriad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was by chance-- by pure chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I receive this letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tell me what-- what happens [? is a ?]-- that they're alive and well in this-- in this particular place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so, of course, we start, you know, celebrating.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my husband went-- after we came to our place where we could sort of establish a little camp, temporarily-- my husband went with somebody else and picked them up and brought them to the Otriad.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were reunited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the story-- yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the story how I got back my sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then we were three sisters.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
